                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-968901967" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="968901967">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/grinner/">丁陌上</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-02-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">施特劳斯学派实现了学术生产的可持续发展。译者使用的术语很古怪。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="936271541">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-936271541" class="vote-count">1</span>
